description:
Today, in NZ I had my first ever piece, a digital glitch video, being shown in an arts festival. In any arts festival ANYWHERE actually. But this was extra cool because I’m in Amsterdam and it was in NZ. So today for my STOREEZ I painted a still from the glitched video. 

In this moment a man is falling and being split into a million pieces while people watch on. He’s going to be caught so it’s ok. 

Personal daily art story
Number 17 #STOREEZ by Cat Brown/ Treasvre Trove
